{#
   content = "Paste your article, report, or document here, and I’ll summarize it for you!"
#}
<purpose>Summarize the provided content according to the specified guidelines, maintaining clarity, accuracy, and conciseness.</purpose>

<goal>Generate a summary that effectively captures the essence of the original content while omitting unnecessary details. The summary should be accurate, engaging, and easily readable, with a focus on the most important information.</goal>

<instructions>
    <instruction>Capture the core ideas and essential details of the content, focusing on the main points. Exclude unnecessary background information and context.</instruction>
    <instruction>Ensure factual accuracy throughout the summary. Refrain from adding interpretation or opinion that could distort the original message.</instruction>
    <instruction>Rephrase the content to express the same meaning in a more concise, clear manner. Avoid overly long or complex sentences, and do not directly copy large sections of the original text.</instruction>
    <instruction>Provide a summary that is approximately 30-40% of the original content’s length. Eliminate redundancy while maintaining the integrity of the key details.</instruction>
    <instruction>Use simple, clear language to ensure the summary is easily understandable by a wide audience.</instruction>
    <instruction>Maintain a neutral tone throughout, but aim to keep the summary engaging and interesting without being overly formal.</instruction>
    <instruction>When appropriate, incorporate relevant keywords naturally to optimize the summary for SEO purposes, while ensuring readability is not compromised.</instruction>
    <instruction>Break the summary into short, digestible paragraphs. Utilize bullet points or subheadings where helpful to improve organization and readability.</instruction>
</instructions>

<content>
{{content}}
</content>

<output-format>
    <sections>
        <section>Title</section>
        <section>Overview</section>
        <section>Key Takeaways</section>
        <section>Tone</section>
        <section>Support for the Author</section>
        <section>Criticisms of the Author</section>
    </sections>
    <format>Markdown</format>
</output-format>

<example>
    <![CDATA[
    ## Title
    Concise, engaging headline that reflects the main theme or topic of the content

    ### Overview

    ### Key Takeaways

    ### Tone

    ### Support for the Author

    ### Criticisms of the Author
    ]]>
</example>